  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Clearing Blade: A Roguelite Adventure for You!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This world, filled with darkness, suffers from the constant invasion of monsters. Over time, many warriors and mages have been defeated or taken captive by the enemy. Now, it’s your turn!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/4502237acbdbcf733fb6c985cd0a2669.poster.avif?t=1734584212\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/4502237acbdbcf733fb6c985cd0a2669.webm?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/4502237acbdbcf733fb6c985cd0a2669.mp4?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Prelude to Battle Begins!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend against the waves of enemies and rescue your comrades who have been captured on the battlefield. The rescued companions will lend you their strength to help you stand against the forces of darkness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/65fdff6f1e27c252d659492babb31511.poster.avif?t=1734584212\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/65fdff6f1e27c252d659492babb31511.webm?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/65fdff6f1e27c252d659492babb31511.mp4?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unite with Your Companions!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join forces with warriors to defeat the enemies and gain amazing abilities. Together, you can overcome any challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/dc94002f5c363a58a4698bb0ebf623cc.poster.avif?t=1734584212\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/dc94002f5c363a58a4698bb0ebf623cc.webm?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/dc94002f5c363a58a4698bb0ebf623cc.mp4?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Never Give Up!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Clearing Blade is a challenging game for gamers around the world who love hack-and-slash and roguelite genres.</i> The controls are easy, but due to the soul-like characteristics, deep strategy is required. Test your skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/979ea509b7ff751d16bf415beb1f0d15.poster.avif?t=1734584212\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/979ea509b7ff751d16bf415beb1f0d15.webm?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/979ea509b7ff751d16bf415beb1f0d15.mp4?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Power of Numbers!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you lack strength, the residents of your base and your companions are ready to help you. Just remember that you will need to prepare <i>a small reward</i> to receive their support!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/9db256952edb232664ea6c3801316d70.poster.avif?t=1734584212\" width=690 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/9db256952edb232664ea6c3801316d70.webm?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/9db256952edb232664ea6c3801316d70.mp4?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are You Ready to Answer the Call of a Hero?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the action of Clearing Blade and carve out your legend as a hero. The battlefield awaits your command!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In early access, you can enjoy the following content:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action-oriented roguelite hack-and-slash with great controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 different characters with unique skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 50 diverse enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 powerful and unique bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 distinct maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roguelite mechanics with saved progress</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the official version, we will enhance stability and gameplay experience through continuous updates based on community feedback. Your participation and opinions will greatly contribute to the development of our game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/312af0f255636ca45569f5fe97bfe3c1.poster.avif?t=1734584212\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/312af0f255636ca45569f5fe97bfe3c1.webm?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/312af0f255636ca45569f5fe97bfe3c1.mp4?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
